quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,59,"Of old sent We Noah to his people, and he said, \"O my people! worship God. Ye have no God but Him: indeed I fear for you the chastisement of the great day"
  7,60,"The chiefs of his people said, \"We clearly see that thou art in a palpable error"
  7,61,"He said, \"There is no error in me, O my people! but I am a messenger from the Lord of the Worlds"
  7,62,"I bring to you the messages of my Lord, and I give you friendly counsel; for I know from God what ye know not"
  7,63,"Marvel ye that a Warning should come to you from your Lord through one of yourselves, that he may warn you, and that ye may fear for yourselves, and that haply ye may find mercy"
  7,64,"But they treated him as a liar: so we delivered him and those who were with him in the ark, and we drowned those who charged our signs with falsehood; for they were a blind people"